FBIS4-48559 "drafr099_d_94017" FBIS-AFR-94-099 Daily Report 22 May 1994 SOUTHERN AFRICA Malawi President's Office Dissolves Parastatal Boards President's Office Dissolves Parastatal Boards EA2305082094 Blantyre Malawi Broadcasting Corporation Network in English 1600 GMT 22 May 94 EA2305082094 Blantyre Malawi Broadcasting Corporation Network English BFN [Text] The office of the president and cabinet [OPC] has announced that all boards of parastatal organizations in the country have been dissolved with immediate effect. In a press release issued in Lilongwe, the OPC said new board members will be appointed in the near future. The announcement said during the interim period, parastatal organizations should contact the Department of Statutory Bodies on any matters which would have been dealt with by the board.
